RequestBody.prompt: acrylic painting of a sunflower with bees

data.revised_prompt: Create an image representing an acrylic artwork, that showcases a vibrant sunflower in full bloom. Around the sunflower, several bees can be seen, collecting nectar and pollinating the flower. The bees are detailed and realistic, buzzing around fervently. The backdrop should be a clear blue sky contrasting with the bright yellow of the sunflower. The composition of the painting is balanced, the sunflower being the centerpiece and the bees adding dynamism to the scene.
